Zimbabwe Ready to Trade Diamonds in ‘Normal Way,’ SUsan Shabangu Says

-- B y   A l a a   S h a h i n e
-- 
2011-04-13T12:30:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/zimbabwe-ready-to-trade-diamonds-in-normal-way-susan-shabangu-says.html
Zimbabwe  has complied with
international standards and is ready to trade diamonds from its
Marange fields in a “normal way,” Susan Shabangu,  South
Africa ’s mines minister, told a diamond conference in Dubai
today.  “We are satisified Zimbabwe has complied,” she said. “It
is unfair to keep Zimbabwe under scrutiny.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
